title: Little Diggers Series Dune Spoon Kid Safe Poly Sand Shovel
description: Dune Spoons are fully functional shovels made just for kids. They make the perfect beach/sand tool and are sure to bring quality family time to your beach vacation or your backyard sandbox. Unlike metal tools, Dune Spoons are built from a soft, yet durable plastic that is kid safe. Dune spoons are offered in bright, vibrant colors that will not rust. Encourage your kids to play outdoors with a Dune Spoon and other Little Diggers kid safe products by Emsco.
